videos.headline: Taylor puts Texas State on the board
videos.description: Anthony Taylor score a touchdown from 5-yards out to put Texas State ahead.

videos.headline: Brown gashes Arkansas State D for big run
videos.description: Robert Brown runs 71 yards to put the Bobcats in the red zone in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Taylor's second TD pulls Texas State closer
videos.description: Anthony Taylor scores from 18 yards out to pull the Bobcats closer in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Edwards high points one for TD
videos.description: Justice Hansen complete pass to Kendrick Edwards for a 12-yard touchdown pass play to extend the lead for Arkansas State.
